{"name":"Sentry","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">The wizard plucks a bit of their mind out like candy floss and leaves it </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">stuck to a wall somewhere. This psychic presence is invisible to the naked </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">eye but extends the wizard&rsquo;s senses to that spot for the duration. While </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">it lasts the wizard suffers -1 to all rolls due to the incredible confusion </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">this generates. If the shard is discovered and harmed the wizard loses 2d6 </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Stamina due to the shock.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"1","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676770544219,"modifiedTime":1676771738844,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"0fb5qchyl4dSXEem","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Assassin's Daggers","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Evocatively named but actually quite mundane. The wizard whispers to an </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">object and that object then seeks out and vigorously and repeatedly bumps </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">into the desired target. Obviously if you whisper to a poisoned dagger the </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">result is one thing while doing it to a letter is another. Travels any distance </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">and always arrives (eventually).</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"3","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676768597944,"modifiedTime":1676771738836,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"2Kemn4CmbwSiL9z2","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
