{"name":"Read Stars","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Rather than physical stars the wizard navigates by astral starlight that </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">peeks through the veil. This Spell enables the wizard to get a reasonable </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">sense of direction regardless of any obscuring factors.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"1","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676770502447,"modifiedTime":1676771738844,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"4f9WsXW4F3SeZBSM","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Thought Vapour","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">The wizard can cause their nose to exist in multiple alternative realities, </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">travel through various Spheres, and enable the olfactory sensation of </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">thought. Emotions, attitudes, and underlying feelings can be smelled. No </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">words or images are formed, just impressions. Any strong odour causes </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">this Spell to fail.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"1","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676770782506,"modifiedTime":1676771738845,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"5kftYKoWRqCqUQqp","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Jolt","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/lightning.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">The mischievous apprentice&rsquo;s favourite Spell, Jolt sends an arc of electricity </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">from the wizard&rsquo;s outstretched hand towards a target. Ignores Armour.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":"2","dr2":"2","dr3":"3","dr4":"3","dr5":"5","dr6":"7","dr7":"9"},"rank":"1","castingCost":"1","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":true},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676769878211,"modifiedTime":1676771738841,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"69TNK0OtTGHsNYo9","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Sleep","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">The wizard convinces a target to forgo wakefulness for a time, causing them </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">to sleep until woken unless they successfully Test their Luck. Remember: </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">fighting is loud.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"2","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676770641722,"modifiedTime":1676771738845,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"78xfMV6852Kupe7z","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Callous Strike","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">The Wizard-Knights are most famous for their remote combat whereby they </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">swing their Silver Swords seemingly at nothing only for their opponents, </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">many metres away, to be torn to tatters. This Spell can be used in place of a </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">melee attack by Rolling Versus as normal and inflicting Damage according </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">to the Weapon used. May only be used against targets within clear sight.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"1","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676768989193,"modifiedTime":1676771738837,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"97XG1TvMfhalctAU","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Farseeing","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Endows the wizard with engorged, plate-like eyes that are able to see in </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">minute detail for miles around but are unable to see anything up close. </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Lasts until ended.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"2","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676769450630,"modifiedTime":1676771738840,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"9LYqQbexAlP8MOnD","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Ember","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">A simple but effective summoning of fire. Flames the size of a small bonfire </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">appear somewhere within 12 metres of the wizard. Once present there is </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">no accounting for its actions.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"2","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676769291271,"modifiedTime":1676771738839,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"Bo1e8pEIAlK0UM73","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Undo","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">The wizard disentangles a Spell from this instance of reality. To do so they</span><br role=\"presentation\"><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">must Roll Versus the original casting if disentanglement is possible at all.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"double cost of original Spell","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674434956209,"modifiedTime":1676771738846,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"CGAE3aIGsU0K2FaX","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Diminish","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Cause something to Test its Luck (or Skill for Enemies) or reduce its size </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">by half. Lasts 3 minutes.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"2","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676769201905,"modifiedTime":1676771738838,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"E5Dw3s9FA4CQtOZK","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Ironhand","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">The common man does not appreciate exactly how close flesh and iron </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">are when considered relative to, say, flesh and the smell of hot tea. With </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">some slight convincing the wizard may cause a target&rsquo;s flesh to behave </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">as though it had the desirable properties of metal. They get +1 Skill and </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">immunity to modestly proportioned fires for 3 minutes.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"3","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676769833701,"modifiedTime":1676771738841,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"FcARsnMmHEjML2Jr","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Exorcism","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">The Red Priests posit that all negative behaviour is a symptom of some </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">level of possession, or at least direct influence, by the forces of Change, </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">unwitting agents of Mass in need of healing. The wizard throws salt at </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">their target and Rolls Versus the possessing spirit to cast it out. In the case </span><span class=\"\" dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">of a Fumble the spirit is drawn into and possesses the wizard.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"1","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676769350430,"modifiedTime":1676771738839,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"FrMHA5H5sf2MKvNO","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Amity","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">The College of Friends always sends out its Factotums on nights after Amity </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">classes. Clearing out the bars and brothels of their drunken apprentices is </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">tiring work. Use of this Spell causes the target to Test their Luck (or Skill </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">for Enemies) or become very friendly towards the wizard, as though they </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">were an old friend. They won&rsquo;t act irrationally, though, and if they were </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">already a bit of a boor this might not change much.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"4","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676768463333,"modifiedTime":1676771738836,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"Frp4vR4nkhBPb0Yj","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Starry Orb","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">The wizard creates a 5-dimensional orb above their head. All intelligent </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">beings looking at it must Test their Luck or marvel at it for 3 minutes.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"4","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676770730288,"modifiedTime":1676771738845,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"GICjlKDqFfjKPXOW","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Skeletal Counsel","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Necromancers often talk to skulls. Sometimes they talk back. Use of this </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Spell enables speaking with the dead, who answer one question per casting. </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Requires a skull.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"3","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676770617384,"modifiedTime":1676771738844,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"GQcWTU5uHGWr9rxu","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Darkness","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Summon a stationary, perfect sphere of darkness up to five metres from </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">the wizard for up to 3 minutes.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"3","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676769148944,"modifiedTime":1676771738838,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"GtSCzdxojr8Ndpdw","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"True Seeing","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">The wizard focuses their sight on the unambiguous truth of matter, </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">enabling them to see through illusions for the next 10 minutes.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"3","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676770922829,"modifiedTime":1676771738846,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"GwiaD3KNEX4BlQWQ","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Assume Shape","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">The wizard undergoes a distressing transformation into an inanimate </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">object no larger than a piano and no smaller than a cup. Lasts until ended.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"4","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676768667876,"modifiedTime":1676771738836,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"IZiZZG0gDqoAfNIK","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Languages","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">The wizard forms a mouth with their hands through which they can speak </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">any language. They can simultaneously cup their other hand to their ear to </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">understand them in return. Lasts for one conversation.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"1","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676769929160,"modifiedTime":1676771738841,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"IeCfGP9ZaF4Q6s9Q","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Peace","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Open up the mind to universal love and cause two subjects to Test their </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Luck (or Skill for Enemies) or cease hostilities. They still defend themselves </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">if attacked but at least appreciate the pettiness of it.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"2","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676770185438,"modifiedTime":1676771738842,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"JHLdrZyKvuf8OOo6","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Brittle Twigs","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">You snap a twig or other brittle object to cause an injury in another. They </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">must Test their Luck (or Skill for Enemies) or suffer a broken bone.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"2","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676768961572,"modifiedTime":1676771738837,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"JkBzX8TaAiVvwxSE","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Exchange Shape","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">What looks like a hug is in fact fell wizardry! The wizard bumps into </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">another and exchanges bodies. Lasts until the wizard chooses to end it but </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">they must be within sight of their own body for this to happen.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"5","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676769320545,"modifiedTime":1676771738839,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"Kob8N0fi4f8QQ1Iy","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Fear","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">In the eyes of one poor target the wizard grows into a primal monster </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">from the depths of their lizard brain. They attempt to flee, and if flight is </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">impossible they curl up in a ball and whimper. They may Test their Luck (or </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Skill for Enemies) to resist the illusion.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"1","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676769476754,"modifiedTime":1676771738840,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"MsZc7NJHTVNcCaz3","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Read Entrails","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">The wizard can get the answer to one question from the entrails of a living </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">creature. The size and importance of the creature influences the level </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">of knowledge gained. Small, common animals are able to offer yes or no </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">answers, oxen can predict things obtusely, lamassu may offer explicit and </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">thorough advice.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"1","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676770475351,"modifiedTime":1676771738844,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"NEqCo3noYkR7khrr","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Grow","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Cause an item to grow half its size again if it fails to Test its Luck (or Skill </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">for Enemies). Lasts for 3 minutes.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"2","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676769680875,"modifiedTime":1676771738840,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"OgmujYeUbgFSt43F","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Astral Reach","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">The Sorcerers of the Academy of Doors are most famous for this one </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Spell. With it they may reach through any portal and into another known </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">receptacle. For example they might use it to reach through to a safe in </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">their manse via their purse. This Spell only allows partial translocation&mdash;</span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">the wizard cannot fully or permanently enter.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"1","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676768706363,"modifiedTime":1676771738836,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"OhYEobMsgujWxGpT","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Slide Skywards","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Requires mirrors or other highly reflective surfaces. The wizard stands </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">between two reflective surfaces so that they are infinitely repeated. </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">They then step out from between them but as a different incidence of </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">themselves. To those watching the wizard moves in the direction not seen </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">and reappears between two mirrors elsewhere. If the location has been </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">compromised the wizard arrives in a random mirrored location somewhere </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">across the million crystal Spheres.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"6","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676770670323,"modifiedTime":1676771738845,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"PPPL70n2vMF2IXDw","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Torpor","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Those who study the dead consider it necessary to develop a profound </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">sympathy with their subject</span> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">&mdash;</span> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">how can you speak with the dead if you </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">don&rsquo;t understand the dead? Torpor helps build post-mortem empathy by </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">causing the necromancer to temporarily die. Bodily functions are halted, </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">no food, water, or air is needed, and they are, by most vulgar definitions</span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">of the word, dead. The Spell lasts until ended by the wizard, who remains </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">vaguely aware of their surroundings to the extent of being conscious of </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">sound and movement but not of what is said or who is saying it. They still </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">take Damage from bodily abuse while under the effect and can indeed </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">become irretrievably dead.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"3","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676770880168,"modifiedTime":1676771738846,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"PViezIESG5KDfPhr","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Teleport","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">The wizard or a target of their choosing may travel to any location within a </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">single Sphere instantly. If unfamiliar with the location they must Test their </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Luck (or Skill for Enemies) or be thrown wildly off course to potentially </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">devastating results.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"10","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676770759111,"modifiedTime":1676771738845,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"PfUItw6upOS4Zz8Z","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Helping Hands","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Animate hands spring forth from an inanimate surface and perform any </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">task the wizard requires but are limited to being rooted to the spot from </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">which they sprang. They last until the wizard wills it or leaves the location.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"1","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676769709810,"modifiedTime":1676771738841,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"PzxzbVcyDyiVvrvS","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Web","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Whether this is opening a portal to the plane of slime or channelling the </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">sprites of sickness, all can agree that it is quite disgusting. The wizard </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">blows forth the &ldquo;web&rdquo; from their nose and all in a cone extending 12 metres </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">in front of the wizard are trapped unless they Test their Luck (or Skill for </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Enemies). Each Turn anything passing through or out of it must repeat the </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Test or become stuck. Dries up after 12 rounds.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"2","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676771003580,"modifiedTime":1676771738846,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"SLrP2CwASoM4vtL1","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Poison","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">When cast upon a liquid this Spell causes it to become deadly poison. The </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">liquid deals 4 Damage if drunk and 1 Damage per Turn until the target </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">successfully Tests their Luck (or Skill for Enemies). The liquid loses its </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">potency after an hour.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"1","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676770217043,"modifiedTime":1676771738843,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"SxwggMSdF87EOOiT","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Posthumous Vitality","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Necromancers, known for their social inadequacy, often find themselves</span><br role=\"presentation\"><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">having to make friends.</span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">This Spell requires a fresh, or at least whole and lubricated, corpse. The </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">wizard rolls 2d6 plus their Posthumous Vitality Skill Total and consults</span><br role=\"presentation\"><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">the following chart (13+ counts for an Advancement tick):</span></p>\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\" border=\"1\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 26.9054%;\"><col style=\"width: 73.0946%;\"></colgroup>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>4-12</td>\n<td>Nothing happens.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>13-14</td>\n<td>The vitality is clumsily applied, causing the body to explode messily. A new one must be found.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>15-16</td>\n<td>The creature is animated and lasts for 24 hours before literally falling to pieces.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>17+</td>\n<td>Perfect reanimation. the creature lasts until destroyed.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"5","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676770245224,"modifiedTime":1676771738843,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"TXmbocW3lpO7dvtb","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Leech","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">The necromancer must place their hands on a living subject and allow their </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">fingertips to transform into sucking apertures which drain the victim of </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">blood. Deal 2d6 Damage to your victim and regain half as much Stamina.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"2","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676769974069,"modifiedTime":1676771738841,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"VHRWeCYXSfxOn1vg","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Drown","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Cause a target&rsquo;s lungs to fill with water. They must Test their Luck (or Skill </span><span dir=\"ltr\" aria-owns=\"pdfjs_internal_id_745R\">for Enemies). If they fail they start to Drown (7.9) and are incapacitated </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">as water pours from their mouth. They may Test again once per Turn until </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">they pass, at which point the Spell ends.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"4","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676769225113,"modifiedTime":1676771738838,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"WYQgMLd1KVPXgo9W","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Presence","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">This Spell creates the sense of being watched by a patriarchal figure. Some </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">find it comforting, others, not so much.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"1","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676770375799,"modifiedTime":1676771738843,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"Wk2UpPgZV10tHPpc","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Befuddle","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">A</span> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">wizard&rsquo;s</span> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">touch</span> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">can</span> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">shake</span> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">up</span> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">someone&rsquo;s</span> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">mind</span> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">like</span> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">a</span> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">snow</span> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">globe. </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">The</span> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">target</span> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">makes</span> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">all</span> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">rolls</span> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">at</span> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">a</span> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">-1</span> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">penalty</span> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">until</span> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">their</span> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">head</span> <span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">clears. </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Lasts for 3 minutes.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"1","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676768863032,"modifiedTime":1676771738837,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"XF67a4z8gvPytXbm","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Find","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">When wizards lose their glasses they mumble to themselves until they </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">turn up. The thing being sought must be a specific object, not a general </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">category or type, and the direction is only given in terms of compass points.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"2","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676769501489,"modifiedTime":1676771738840,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"XyBnj5jJPNMKdkFT","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Levitate","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Elevates the wizard or another on the backs of tiny invisible sprites who</span><br role=\"presentation\"><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">answer only to their summoner. May float about for 3 minutes.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"2","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676770001120,"modifiedTime":1676771738842,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"YDnmfSAd6mKalyFa","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Flash","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">The wizard claps neatly and issues forth the light of a thousand suns from </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">their hands. All within 20 metres must Test their Luck (or Skill for Enemies) </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">or be blinded for 1d6 minutes.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"3","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676769553228,"modifiedTime":1676771738840,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"YQb7smbXkvU0BLEz","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Cockroach","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">A popular Spell that turns troublesome folk into humiliated animals. The </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">target must Test their Luck (or Skill for Enemies) or be turned into an </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">insignificant creature of the wizard&rsquo;s choice. Lasts forever.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"5","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676769089482,"modifiedTime":1676771738838,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"ZBL6RLEnq1FddVyj","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Wall of Power","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">What they call a wall is in fact a dome, but wizards always have worked in </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">mysterious ways. The wall is a shimmering bubble that causes 1d6 Damage </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">when touched. Nothing may pass without the wizard&rsquo;s permission (it is </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">recommended that they remember to allow air). Lasts for 12 minutes.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"2","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676770972720,"modifiedTime":1676771738846,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"ZrubTKPhVWXhxPnH","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Life Line","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Created by the Horizon Knights to enable them to take the fight to the </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Nothing, they would cast this on their squires and dive off the edge of </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">creation. While this Spell lasts, the wizard&rsquo;s essential bodily functions are </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">linked to another, thereby enabling them to breath or eat for the recipient. </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">They need to breathe and eat for two, which makes it hard to do anything </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">useful while linked. The Spell lasts for a day, until cancelled, or until the </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">death of the linked person. Note if the linked person dies, starves, or is </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">choked you suffer equally.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"1","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676770020119,"modifiedTime":1676771738842,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"ZzU033c8YwQOYRnf","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Natter","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">As everyone knows, wizards are excellent ventriloquists, so good, in fact, </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">that they can throw their voice inside another&rsquo;s mouth. They can target </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">anyone within sight and transmit a short sentence.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"1","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676770136733,"modifiedTime":1676771738842,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"b8D146hJ8o8oKVxK","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Open","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">The wizard chooses a reality wherein the lock was open all along. May be </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">used to open any mundane door or container and counteract a Lock Spell.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"1","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676770163294,"modifiedTime":1676771738842,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"bj2EDdhkQJGkTpV9","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Affix","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-95655f34-7fff-c9ce-bad4-f83454db0015\" dir=\"ltr\">Cause a subject to be fixed in place. While they are so held they do not</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">move, breathe, fall, perspire, acquire, or otherwise change. They are totally</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">immune to harm, in fact. Lasts for 3 minutes.</p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"3","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1673720934918,"modifiedTime":1676771738835,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"eHS0XLjc52CmCDtP","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Invisibility","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">The wizard turns flesh into refractive crystal sheets. It&rsquo;s very uncomfortable </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">and you make a slight shish-ing sound as you move but are quite invisible </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">and don&rsquo;t suffer from the usual limitations of illusions. Lasts for 3 minutes </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">after which you noisily reform into dull and frustratingly opaque flesh.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"3","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676769806592,"modifiedTime":1676771738841,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"fRpHCqzb6HkBqnrq","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Ward","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">A handy Spell only requiring the flick of a wrist. In response to being fired </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">upon the wizard may cast this Spell to cause the missile to be deflected.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"1","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676770946497,"modifiedTime":1676771738846,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"fx4Gj1ndHjKdfUrO","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Hurricane","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">The wizard waves their hands in the air like they just don&rsquo;t care, which, </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">being wizards, they likely don&rsquo;t. A mighty gust knocks everyone over </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">within 30 metres who fails to Test their Luck (or Skill for Enemies), dealing </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">1d3 Damage and making an awful mess. Lasts for 10 minutes. Test Luck </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">every Turn if not taking cover or else take further Damage.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"5","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676769724499,"modifiedTime":1676771738841,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"gtnpiGTx18sDdzVO","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Illusion","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Those viewing this illusion may Test their Luck (or Skill for Enemies) to </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">unveil the trickery. Lasts until the wizard leaves or falls asleep.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"2 (per viewer)","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676769760837,"modifiedTime":1676771738841,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"h9yn92zF2STrhxpr","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Explode","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">So simple that it&rsquo;s arguably not even a Spell but rather a premeditated </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">failure of catastrophic proportions. The wizard causes a one cubic metre </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">object to explode and deal Damage to everyone within 24 metres depending </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">on proximity. Those within 6 metres take Damage as a Gigantic Beast, </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">within 12 as a Large Beast, 18 as a Modest Beast and 24 as a Small Beast.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"5","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676769389361,"modifiedTime":1676771738839,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"j6D3il7BOls2OY3y","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Earthquake","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">The wizard hikes up their wizard robe and stomps their wizard feet. An </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">area 30 metres around them suffers a massive earthquake. Everyone must </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Test their Luck (or Skill for Enemies) or fall through a crack in the earth, </span><span dir=\"ltr\" aria-owns=\"pdfjs_internal_id_746R\">taking falling Damage and being stuck in a bloody great big hole (7.8.1). </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Buildings may be wrecked unless especially sturdy.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"5","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676769263323,"modifiedTime":1676771738839,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"jSH4BnYYR8F5EPZX","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Gills","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">The wizard may permanently gift a touched subject with gills, replacing </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">their usual breathing arrangement if they fail to Test their Luck (or Skill </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">for Enemies). Useful for underwater excursions but less so when inflicted </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">upon a chap in the middle of town. The wizard may end this at will.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"3","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676769648050,"modifiedTime":1676771738840,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"lMPkOU2yPeLwmq9h","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Breach","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">The wizard&rsquo;s hands work elemental material as though it were soft clay. </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Fire, stone, goo, earth, fog, all of it behaves like clay under their touch. </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Lasts for 9 minutes.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"2","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676768925169,"modifiedTime":1676771738837,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"lb6m4mcIZilyGuVU","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Light","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Create an ethereal orb of light that glows like a torch. Lasts 6 hours and </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">can be extinguished at will.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"1","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676770069855,"modifiedTime":1676771738842,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"nVXNsfNq1C9obk3i","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Thunder","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">The wizard raises their arms and shouts something suitably ominous. All </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">within 24 metres must Test their Luck (or Skill for Enemies) or be deafened </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">by a riotous roll of thunder. Luck or no, they are mightily impressed.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"2","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676770819938,"modifiedTime":1676771738845,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"oaaBJZf0i4bVVLJC","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Blood Shroud","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Smear a small amount of a demon&rsquo;s blood on yourself to become completely </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">invisible to them, even if you attack or speak to them, for 6 hours.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"4","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676768902389,"modifiedTime":1676771738837,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"pQrGEPBrpwCncFN1","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Lock","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Magically lock an object. The object must have a lockable aspect to it but </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">is now magically sealed. Permanent until undone or dismissed.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"1","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676770086395,"modifiedTime":1676771738842,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"qs2QiDlAN5yPwvdL","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Darksee","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">The wizard reaches into their sockets and extricates their eyes. Thus freed, </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">the dark void behind can see perfectly well in pitch blackness and suffer </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">excruciating pain in light (-4 penalty to all rolls). Be careful not to lose </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">those eyeballs as re-inserting them is the only way to end the Spell.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"1","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676769177518,"modifiedTime":1676771738838,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"rJ7taHjen8Om43VE","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Cone of Air","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Creates a mysterious and specifically shaped cone of air focused on a </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">touched target&rsquo;s head. They may continue to breathe the freshest of air </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">for 12 minutes.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"2","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676769125586,"modifiedTime":1676771738838,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"sV4exD9aE0MxZVHV","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Babble","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">The wizard speaks nonsense while watching the intended target, causing </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">their words to trip and confuse. This may be done under their breath and </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">relatively subtly.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"2","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676768771448,"modifiedTime":1676771738836,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"t7Bs5U3jt3sn12Yk","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Purple Lens","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">The recipient&rsquo;s eyes glow purple as they experience an alternative reality </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">where people are kind, their surroundings are beautiful, their food is </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">indulgent, and so on. This doesn&rsquo;t change the reality of things but it does </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">make them more palatable. Lasts until they want it to end.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"1","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676770424094,"modifiedTime":1676771738844,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"tFfNYcy37g7tzsG5","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Shatter","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">The wizard may wildly gesticulate at a brittle object no larger than an </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">umbrella and cause it to shatter into a million pieces. Living targets may </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Test their Luck to avoid this unpleasant Spell.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"3","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676770583081,"modifiedTime":1676771738844,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"tI7wpvvromKfCO1H","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Banish Spirit","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">The wizard explains, clearly, sternly, why it is impossible that the spirit </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">could be here at this time. The spirit must Test its Luck (or Skill for </span><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Enemies) or be sent to somewhere less improbable.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"6","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676768814723,"modifiedTime":1676771738837,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"ulJ1egDlktYvFnth","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
{"name":"Quench","type":"spell","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","system":{"name":"","description":"<p><span dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Snuff a small flame with the wave of a hand.</span></p>","attack":{"dr1":2,"dr2":2,"dr3":2,"dr4":2,"dr5":4,"dr6":8,"dr7":10},"rank":"1","castingCost":"1","modifier":"0","improvement":false,"canAttack":false},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"troika","systemVersion":"0.2.7","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1676770450137,"modifiedTime":1676771738844,"lastModifiedBy":"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq"},"_id":"vOG7HtuuCrbFvx9T","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"iubUFLpmPB0vkjXq":3}}
